{"tid":1063120,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"學者聯署警告電磁場致癌風險 籲規管AirPods等無綫設備","createTime":"2019-03-15T14:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T04:53:17.000Z","uid":41420,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a5bc6ea3f7270db6b61fbbcdef6b7fc51859739f","tid":1063120,"uid":41420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:05:52.000Z","msg":"19:17 2019/03/13<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來自全球41個國家，近250名科學家和醫生聯署去信聯合國及世界衛生組織（WHO），要求提防無綫設備發出的幅射對生物的影響。有學者認為，AirPods等無綫藍牙入耳式耳機因為會令頭部組織曝露於更多射頻輻射中，而構成更高的致癌風險。<br />\n<br />\n聯署學者表示，「嚴重擔憂」由電子產品和無綫設備產生的、無處不在並日益增長的電磁場。他們提到，國際癌症研究機構（International Agency for Research on Cancer）分別在2002年和2011年提出關於極低頻電磁場射頻輻射的分類，其中界定電磁場是人類可疑致癌原。<br />\n<br />\n聯署學者批評WHO雖然採納有關分類，但WHO認為未有足夠證據證明，而未有降低電磁場曝露指標。聯署學者要求加強電磁場的規管及相關標準，告知大眾相關風險，建立無輻射區域等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://imoney.hket.com/article/2292107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimoney.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2292107&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=7cc67fae\" target=\"_blank\">http://imoney.hket.com/article/2292107</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bdde28f2d69d80a975e5713f304d3c5286b9b0","tid":1063120,"uid":49136,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"蕉都有輻射啦<br />\n乜都驚不如返石器時代"},{"pid":"a6c943e89e2bd00fdd30f1d95519b5f290589cae","tid":1063120,"uid":41420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e59c894b8888d26881263d6b685151f486425a","tid":1063120,"uid":36673,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"【Fact Check】「專家」憂 AirPods 致癌高危？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1061069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1061069</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5fa679874842d8d70d35bc24a37a6ecfb1c75f31","tid":1063120,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"又屈APPLE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f6050c6ff5416f39219c90d275a2ad9e1b5185","tid":1063120,"uid":20449,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:46:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ec579acb48a44e7733f46de6b048cd8e5965166","tid":1063120,"uid":26082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:53:12.000Z","msg":"iqos都禁得，唔監管，一刀切<br />\nAirPods呢d野都一樣要一刀切<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9c14682206ad2440bd2c0a3a962dd1843764f3","tid":1063120,"uid":41420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02e59c894b8888d26881263d6b685151f486425a","tid":1063120,"uid":36673,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"【Fact Check】「專家」憂 AirPods 致癌高危？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1061069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1061069</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:59:27.000Z","msg":"長知識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554801b4b573f27d8cbe072a73a23e16723a05ff","tid":1063120,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5804a384c08f7986a1f491c2f03fb9454d9d5666","tid":1063120,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"而家成車都二手藍芽<br />\n俾人射死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e8227e9392f3ac886c0534ca5020e3e9458c80","tid":1063120,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{